item.title: First Post
item.description: Just got this thing set up. I’m not going to lie it was kinda a pain in the ass. That’s mostly my fault though because of how I approached things. I saw this theme and I really liked it so I wanted to use it. The only problem is my only experience with GitHub pages was from years ago and I didn’t really like it. Revisiting it after so long was… jarring to say the least and adjusting to new deploy tools like Hugo was surely something.
